original_title: Once Upon A Time 9: The Forest Inn
overview: This forest inn has a very unusual menu: Linne ala carte, Olga grande trio, Marina speciale, Marella stagione, Nina appetizer en Karin, Rita, Sabina specialty of the day... Then, when you notice the exquisitely pretty Kaia in the kitchen, there is absolutely no doubt anymore. This has to be another tantalizing Once Upon A Time production!
title: Once Upon A Time 9: The Forest Inn
